name: Wasted Drank #89
description:
ONLY 1 MINTED of the first 100 Wasted Dranks for 5 tez each. Wasted Dranks live in all of us. They always have a good time by destroying themselves a little too much. Smoke, drink, party at any time day or night — they don't care.
